5
One Move Captures Black (9)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par To be correct, this problem should be called, 'three moves capture black'.
\par
\par After you find the first move, the next move is natural.
\par
\par However, please be careless, thinking you can capture black anyway.
\par }
