Diagram 4 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\fbidis\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\ltrpar\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is the vital point for killing black.
\par
\par When black answers it at 2, white naturally fills black's eyespace with 3. No more explanation is necessary.
\par }
